            # Stack ‚Äî What Is It?

            A **stack** is a **linear data structure** that follows the principle:

            **LIFO**

            **Last In, First Out**

            The last element added to the stack  
            is the **first one removed**.

            mermaid
            graph TD;
              A["Bottom"] --> B;
              B --> C;
              C --> D["Top"];
            /mermaid
